lead_paragraph: Chelsea's Premier League game at Manchester City is a good chance to show they have rediscovered their best form following last season's problems, manager Antonio Conte said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Man City Clash a Chance for Chelsea to Prove Themselves-Conte
